# FSEChat
A real time chatting app built with Node, Express, MongoDB and AngularJS

***
# Usage
Clone the FSEChat Repo [FSEChat](https://github.com/QSSS/FSEChat.git)

Open your **command line tool** from `/FSEChat` and Run `npm install` and `bower install`

Then Do `node server`

Go to `http://localhost:5001` by using your web browser
***
